												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[LOGAN] [SCENE] Nightsong scoops Lorroakan up and overhead presses his near-dead body. She idles, turning around as she delivers her lines to let the world see what she does to those who do ill. Lorroakan is straining his last bit of energy to resist."
